      "title": "Three presidential media directors",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dhanushka Ramanayake, Presidential Media Director (Print Media) Piyasena Dissanayake, and Shanuka Karunaratne, Presidential Media Director (Electronic Media) have been appointed as Presidential Media Director General."
